This folder (e.g. fnurpel_build_env_se_tn_gride_hs) is assumed to be named
according the pattern
  <composite>_build_env_<country code>_<site abreviation>_<security domain>
that is
  fnurpel_build_env_se_tn_gride_hs
is intended for the composite "fnurpel" and configured for country "se", site
"tn", and security domain "gride_hs" (any slases are replaced with '_').

The file dot.buildenvironment should be renamed as
.buildenvironment
and placed in the root of the build-env repo.

The repo is also assumed to contain a folder named SECI that
contain .seci-files. Some examples are provided in the SECI
folder.
